00:05:20.902 --> 00:05:22.820
dertseylt mir a bisl fun Shavl.

00:05:22.860 --> 00:05:24.376
di STORES

00:05:24.376 --> 00:05:26.819
iz geven in gantsn dray kristlekhe

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:29.379
un ale yidishe.

00:05:29.424 --> 00:05:32.540
di groyse gold gesheftn, kleyder gesheftn

00:05:32.985 --> 00:05:34.636
restoranen

00:05:34.636 --> 00:05:36.118
alts yidishe geven.

00:05:37.237 --> 00:05:39.290
s'iz dortn geven a hoypt industrye?

00:05:39.530 --> 00:05:40.775
ya. s'iz geven

00:05:41.051 --> 00:05:43.357
ale yidishe fabrikn. s'iz geven

