hot er gelebt in Shavl, gehat a

00:05:51.783 --> 00:05:52.942
hot er gehat azoy

00:05:53.994 --> 00:05:55.136
a

00:05:55.243 --> 00:05:56.672
a shukh fabrik

00:05:56.998 --> 00:05:58.494
a leder fabrik

