di yidishe kehile, der kongres der yidisher, iz geforn in Kovne

00:07:21.153 --> 00:07:23.240
baym minis-, baym prezident, un m'hot

00:07:23.347 --> 00:07:25.738
arayngeshikt ⟨in⟩ armey, m'hot zey arestirt.

