velkhe shprakh flegt ir redn in der heym?

00:08:46.018 --> 00:08:47.177
yidish.

00:08:48.819 --> 00:08:49.978
bloyz yidish?

00:08:49.882 --> 00:08:50.585
ya.

00:08:51.165 --> 00:08:52.276
nor der tate

00:08:52.276 --> 00:08:56.728
gevelt dertseyln vos di mamen az mir zoln nit farshteyn, hobn zey geredt oyf rusish

00:08:57.898 --> 00:08:58.753
hot

00:08:57.898 --> 00:08:59.631
vayl er iz dokh geven fun Rusland.

