00:09:01.813 --> 00:09:02.612
neyn.

00:09:02.612 --> 00:09:06.937
kh'hob zikh nit oysgelernt. ikh hob zikh gelernt dan az di rusn zaynen arayn in fertsiktn yor.

00:09:08.597 --> 00:09:15.156
un bay undz, di INTELIGENTNE mentshn, di apteykers UNK un di LAWYERS, hobn zey geredt tsvishn zikh rusish.

00:09:17.152 --> 00:09:18.969
mir hobn geredt litvish.

00:09:20.679 --> 00:09:23.325
bashraybt mir vi s'iz geven shabes

00:09:23.345 --> 00:09:24.875
in der ho-, in hoyz.

00:09:24.138 --> 00:09:26.950
shabes iz geven, m'hot nit getort keyn zakh ton.

00:09:27.716 --> 00:09:30.461
mame flegt altsding oyskokhn, shtel a tsholnt

