00:09:52.320 --> 00:09:54.188
dos fleg ikh oyfesn, ober

00:09:54.446 --> 00:09:55.515
befor

00:09:55.515 --> 00:10:02.366
der tate iz nit gekumen fun shul fraytik tsu nakht hot zi undz nit gegebn keyn esn. m'hot nit ge- ikh fleg hobn a DATE, fleg ikh nit torn aroysgeyn.

00:10:02.411 --> 00:10:04.110
flegt mir hitn vi a ganev.

00:10:05.988 --> 00:10:07.704
vayl s'iz geven shabes.

00:10:07.120 --> 00:10:07.890
ya.

00:10:09.077 --> 00:10:10.331
flegt ir hobn

00:10:10.331 --> 00:10:11.251
⟨gasts⟩?

00:10:11.270 --> 00:10:12.395
tsu shabes

00:10:12.452 --> 00:10:14.049
