mayn mame's mame hot geheysn

00:23:37.015 --> 00:23:39.003
Lane, un der z-

00:23:39.077 --> 00:23:41.080
un der zeyde hot geheysn Notl.

00:23:41.439 --> 00:23:44.651
mayn tate's olevasholem hot geheysn Yitskhok

00:23:44.651 --> 00:23:46.378
un zi hot geheysn Hene.

00:23:47.075 --> 00:23:49.173
un vu hobn zey ale gevoynt

00:23:49.173 --> 00:23:50.833
akhuts di in Rusland?

00:23:51.632 --> 00:23:54.445
zey hobn gelebt in a kleyne shtetl, in Shidlove.

00:23:55.158 --> 00:23:56.941
ober zey zaynen umgekumen bef-

00:23:57.183 --> 00:24:00.586
befor ikh bin gekumen oyf der velt.

00:23:59.057 --> 00:24:00.553
iz er umgekumen?

00:24:00.812 --> 00:24:03.169
m'hot zey, dem zeydn hot men oyfgehangen

00:24:03.512 --> 00:24:05.700
vayl er hot gehat a, er iz geven zeyer raykh

00:24:05.992 --> 00:24:10.200
un ven di rusishe SOLDIERS zaynen arayn in zi- zekhtsntn yor, in

00:24:10.200 --> 00:24:11.302
fuftsntn yor

00:24:12.455 --> 00:24:14.829
zaynen arayn di kozakn un gezogt

00:24:14.919 --> 00:24:17.529
az zey hobn gegebn di daytshn hober

00:24:17.872 --> 00:24:19.216
er hot afile nit gevust

00:24:19.425 --> 00:24:23.115
di daytshn zaynen nokh nit geven in z- in fuftsntn yor, ikh veys nit.

00:24:24.453 --> 00:24:26.860
un m'hot im oyfgehangen, vayl er

00:24:27.677 --> 00:24:29.021
er ⟨iz dokh⟩ geven a yid

00:24:30.630 --> 00:24:35.164
ober der soldat vos hot im oyfgehangen, ho- hobn di eygene soldatn im geshosn.

00:24:36.047 --> 00:24:37.104
azoy arum az

00:24:37.548 --> 00:24:39.600
⟨mer hobn mir nit ge-⟩

00:24:37.565 --> 00:24:40.479
un vos iz gevorn m- mit zayn vayb, mit UNK

00:24:39.600 --> 00:24:44.895
di vayb iz geven aroysgefirt tsulib di UNK aroysgefirt in Rusland, un mayn mamen mit

00:24:44.895 --> 00:24:46.723
der tantn, mit a onkl

00:24:46.813 --> 00:24:51.347
avekgefirt in Rusland, un dortn hot zi zikh bakent mit mayn tate un hot khasene gehat dort.

00:24:52.770 --> 00:24:56.072
un di bobe iz frier gekumen mit di tante mitn onkl

00:24:56.550 --> 00:24:59.580
hot zi lang nit gelebt, efsher a yor, un zi iz oykh geshtorbn.

00:25:00.735 --> 00:25:04.881
vi azoy iz zent di eltern arayn keyn Shavl?

00:25:05.645 --> 00:25:09.014
mir zaynen aribergeforn fun, fun Shidlove in Shavl.

00:25:09.347 --> 00:25:10.415
far vos ober?

00:25:11.619 --> 00:25:13.110
merer tsu fardinen.

00:25:13.110 --> 00:25:16.440
un mir hobn gedarft hobn merer SCHOOL far di kinder.

00:25:17.627 --> 00:25:18.932
hobn gelebt zeyer

00:25:18.932 --> 00:25:20.473
azoy hobn mir gelebt in Shavl.

00:25:21.238 --> 00:25:23.122
mir hobn opgelebt a tsayt in Shavl.

00:25:24.191 --> 00:25:27.155
hobn di eltern gehat brider un shvester?

00:25:27.701 --> 00:25:30.514
ya, mayn mame hot gehat a shvester un a bruder.

00:25:30.620 --> 00:25:35.204
un zey hobn gehat kinder. di daytshn hobn avekgeharget zey dem ershtn tog vi zey zaynen gekumen.

00:25:35.784 --> 00:25:37.871
zey hobn gelebt in Shidlove.

00:25:35.801 --> 00:25:36.538
vi

00:25:38.163 --> 00:25:39.963
vi hobn geheysn

00:25:40.239 --> 00:25:42.785
mayn tante hot geheysn Khaye

00:25:42.785 --> 00:25:44.689
un mayn onkl hot geheysn Berl.

00:25:45.369 --> 00:25:47.237
un vifl kinder hobn zey gehat?

00:25:47.107 --> 00:25:52.350
di tante hot gehat a yingl mit a meydl. ikh gedenk gornit vi zey hobn geheysn. un der onkl hot gehat eyn yingl.

00:25:53.452 --> 00:25:55.230
un oyf der tate's zayt

00:25:55.275 --> 00:25:56.687
shvester un brider?

00:25:59.561 --> 00:26:03.403
er hot gehat shvestern un brider, ober ikh, ikh ken zey nit.

00:26:05.467 --> 00:26:07.335
ir ve- ir kent di nemen?

00:26:09.112 --> 00:26:12.701
di nemen, a bisl ken ikh, vayl der tate flegt dertseyln.

00:26:13.010 --> 00:26:15.654
s'iz geven Mashe, un s'iz geven

00:26:15.744 --> 00:26:17.544
Pesye un

00:26:17.668 --> 00:26:19.856
un Toybe iz geven

00:26:21.515 --> 00:26:23.233
Beyle iz geven epes

00:26:23.233 --> 00:26:24.091
gedenk nit.

00:26:26.021 --> 00:26:27.233
un vu hobn zey ge-

00:26:27.253 --> 00:26:28.175
gelebt?

00:26:27.320 --> 00:26:29.052
gelebt in Smargon.

00:26:29.430 --> 00:26:30.504
vu iz dos?

00:26:30.493 --> 00:26:31.820
lebn Minsk.

00:26:32.501 --> 00:26:33.629
a vayter veg

00:26:33.629 --> 00:26:35.364
fun SIAUL- fun Shavl?

00:26:35.100 --> 00:26:36.782
dos iz nit vayt fun Vilne.

00:26:37.547 --> 00:26:38.318
epes a

00:26:38.458 --> 00:26:40.477
a tsen kilometer, fuftsn kilometer.

00:26:41.006 --> 00:26:46.839
hot i- akhuts di shvester brider un eltern, hobn i- hot ir gehat andere kroyvim in Shavl?

00:26:47.520 --> 00:26:48.780
in Shavl?

00:26:48.937 --> 00:26:49.775
neyn.

00:26:50.709 --> 00:26:52.847
Shavl hobn mir nit gehat keyn kroyvim.

00:26:53.088 --> 00:26:55.884
hobn gehat in Afrike UNK di gantse mishpokhe.

00:26:58.185 --> 00:27:00.407
di mame hot gehat akht onkls in Afrike.

00:27:01.374 --> 00:27:02.651
un COUSINS.

00:27:03.703 --> 00:27:09.519
nor di eyn tante hot gelebt in Shidlove, di vos hot nit gekent avekforn in Afrike, m'hot nit derlozt.

00:27:08.867 --> 00:27:12.945
iz zent ir geven mit zey in farbindung? hot ir zey a mol gezen?

00:27:11.381 --> 00:27:13.164
ya, fun Afrike?

00:27:13.220 --> 00:27:15.408
zey flegn undz shikn ale monat gelt.

00:27:21.219 --> 00:27:23.053
dertseylt mir a bisl

00:27:23.126 --> 00:27:26.895
fun ayer arbet. ir zogt az ir hot gearbet in kongres?

00:27:26.383 --> 00:27:27.047
ya.

00:27:26.906 --> 00:27:28.065
ven hot i-

00:27:27.058 --> 00:27:29.162
in yidishe kehile hob ikh gearbet.

00:27:29.133 --> 00:27:31.524
ven hot ir ongehoybn tsu arbetn dortn?

00:27:32.255 --> 00:27:36.316
kh'hob ongefangen als kind, ikh muz zayn a yor tsen.

00:27:36.390 --> 00:27:38.004
alts a shik meydele.

00:27:38.178 --> 00:27:41.716
zey hobn mir zeyer lib gehat, vayl ikh hob gearbet in kinder gortn.

00:27:42.650 --> 00:27:46.458
ikh bin geven di TEACHER. az ikh fleg aroysgeyn shpatsirn mit di kinder, hot men oyfge-

00:27:46.768 --> 00:27:50.121
hob ikh zikh geshemt, vayl ikh bin nit geven greser fun di kinder.

00:27:51.476 --> 00:27:54.255
hob ikh gebetn dem PRINCIPAL fun SCHOOL

00:27:54.395 --> 00:27:56.566
az ikh vil nit arbetn mer, hot er mir

00:27:56.775 --> 00:27:59.554
"veyst vos, RAYA? vest esn bay undz SUPPER,

00:28:01.280 --> 00:28:03.333
ober shtey nor biz ende yor."

00:28:03.727 --> 00:28:07.147
un di, in ⟨di zelbn koridor⟩ iz geven di yidishe kehile.

00:28:08.537 --> 00:28:11.248
hobn zey mir tsugekhapt tsu arbetn, iz

00:28:11.304 --> 00:28:13.664
hobn zey mir geshikt far a shik meydl, un nokh dem

00:28:13.700 --> 00:28:16.175
hekher un hekher biz ikh bin gevorn a BOOKKEEPER.

00:28:19.387 --> 00:28:21.300
hob ikh opgearbet dortn a tsayt.

00:28:23.842 --> 00:28:27.481
iz geven a geveyntlekhe zakh az a froy zol arbetn?

00:28:27.639 --> 00:28:28.595
ya.

00:28:28.972 --> 00:28:31.059
gearbet mit mir nokh a meydl oykhet.

00:28:31.740 --> 00:28:32.792
mit undz hobn gearbet

00:28:32.837 --> 00:28:35.683
nit eyns, tsvey, dray, dray mener hobn gearbet.

00:28:36.363 --> 00:28:40.660
tsi zaynen dortn geven politishe oder tsienistishe organizatsyes?

00:28:39.890 --> 00:28:40.694
ya.

00:28:41.173 --> 00:28:43.412
s'iz geven der SCOUT,

00:28:43.721 --> 00:28:45.403
C. di

00:28:46.033 --> 00:28:51.124
un s'iz geven C. S. un s'iz geven BETAR. Zhabotinski iz geven bay undz gekumen

00:28:52.850 --> 00:28:54.257
un

00:28:53.137 --> 00:28:54.414
ir hot im gezen?

00:28:54.257 --> 00:28:54.836
ya.

00:28:54.977 --> 00:28:57.773
er iz gegangen in a broynem SUIT mit shtivelekh

00:28:59.347 --> 00:29:01.462
mit di gantse uniform iz er gegangen.

00:29:01.462 --> 00:29:03.038
⟨gehaltn⟩ a rede far zey.

00:29:03.060 --> 00:29:04.624
in velkhn yor iz dos geven?

